@{ ViewBag.Title = "Privacy Policy"; }
<div style="max-width:700px;margin:40px auto;padding:24px;font-family:Segoe UI,Arial,sans-serif;">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>This Privacy Policy explains how SavourSA collects, uses, and protects your information when you use our platform.</p>
    <h3>Information we collect</h3>
    <p>Account details (name, email, phone, province), content you share (recipes, comments, favourites), and technical data needed to keep your account secure.</p>
    <h3>How we protect it</h3>
    <p>Passwords are hashed and never stored in plain text. Verification codes and password reset tokens expire automatically and can only be used once.</p>
    <h3>Sharing</h3>
    <p>We do not sell your personal information to third parties. Data is only used to operate and improve the SavourSA platform.</p>
